thread.title: J Kerr
thread.title_full: Country House Outdoor reviewed by J Kerr

author: J Kerr
title: J Kerr
text: My Fjallraven backpack is excellent. Not a brand you see around much but excellent quality and Country House Outdoor supplied it for a very competitive price. Prompt delivery with no problems, I'll definately use them again and will call in next time I'm in Carlisle.
